Package filipondiosUtils

Class FormattedNumber

java.lang.Object
filipondiosUtils.FormattedNumber
All Implemented Interfaces:
Comparable<FormattedNumber>
public class FormattedNumber extends Object implements Comparable<FormattedNumber>
Class that creates objets symulating fraction numbers and int numbers by parsing a String input with or without the character "/". This allows to the user to type any number as n/m or n.
Version:
07.06.2022
Author:
Filipondios
